Deafened - goorgira

Stumble, trip while walking - tar'quli - ܬܲܪܩܘܼܠܹܐ
- tar'qalta

Shuffling, dragging in a sloppy way - ship'paship - ܫܸܦܵܫܸܦ

Root of: to quake, to tremble, to vibrate, to throb, to twang - nod - ܢܘܕ

Quivering, trembling, shaking, shivering - noda - ܢܲܘܕܵܐ
