Lazy, weak, soft - nshisha - ܢܫܝܼܫܵܐ

Insensible, indifferent, unaware, insensitive - lamitragshana - ܠܵܐܡܸܬܪܲܓܫܵܢܵܐ

Intelligent, clever, quick to learn - ia'loopa - ܝܲܠܘܼܦܵܐ

To stare, gaze, contemplate - pa'karta - ܦܵܟܲܪܬܵܐ

Staring, looking - pakoora

