A step, a footstep, a pace - pa'shoota - ܦܵܨܘܿܥܬܵܐ

To press, to add pressure to, covering heavily as to cause pressure upon the body - maad’iushi - ܡܲܕܝܘܼܫܹܐ

Squinting, squint-eyed, cross-eyed - wira - ܘܸܪܵܐ
