Abnormal, peculiar, strange - shniza - ܫܢܝܼܙܵܐ

Drowsiness, a very light sleep - noma - ܢܵܘܡܵܐ

Shy, nervous, timid, fearful - qa'nita - ܩܲܢܝܼܛܵܐ

